IngeTrazo — authors and contributors
=====================================

Creator and lead author
------------------------
Marco Sumari Tellez <ing.sumari@gmail.com>
    Civil Engineer, Lima, Peru.
    Original author and designer of IngeTrazo; wrote the topology engine,
    tools, rendering, and file formats.

